{"tid":1109424,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"港姐三甲只餘「清泉」  朱千雪或成最大贏家！同屆冠軍「失蹤」亞軍今被揭搭兩船","createTime":"2019-04-16T09:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T02:20:37.000Z","uid":9573,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"84a3012d475c1dd3d94e4887a847231d0016c1b0","tid":1109424,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:20:12.000Z","msg":"「非凡絕色40載 令你大開眼界」。如今一句「令你大開眼界」似乎所言非虛！在2012年第40屆香港小姐決賽當晚早被視為「民選冠軍」，挾著民意卻在最後關頭輸掉給伺服器故障的朱千雪，隨著同屆亞軍黃心穎被揭與許志安一腳搭兩船，2012年香港小姐三甲其中幾近成為唯一「清泉」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/147/d147020.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F147%2Fd147020.jpg&h=9e61bcc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年在最後階段本以互動程式讓觀眾票選，但伺服器不堪大量瞬間瀏覽而崩潰，主辦方於是改由評判決出三甲，結果選出冠軍張名雅，亞軍黃心穎，季軍朱千雪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/213021/org/0e48a9a7c5d7e97bb66bc76a7fafe07b.jpg/drsSQQ_owkWiqHQxx6SldTj4Ily7PD4RooGnUKKBp1A?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F213021%2Forg%2F0e48a9a7c5d7e97bb66bc76a7fafe07b.jpg%2FdrsSQQ_owkWiqHQxx6SldTj4Ily7PD4RooGnUKKBp1A%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=6556dafb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早被視為「民選冠軍」的朱千雪賽後乘著氣勢入行，獲高層力挺接拍多部港劇和綜藝節目，因此被指有「後台照顧」。有傳惹張黃二人不滿，更擬聯手杯葛，不和之說甚囂塵上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/212995/org/fe2877e964684cf6180457372c1f3037.jpg/abu9XXHgY3w6h-SY76A9pNQ8JW-6nbMSaXgCOGl4Ajg?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F212995%2Forg%2Ffe2877e964684cf6180457372c1f3037.jpg%2Fabu9XXHgY3w6h-SY76A9pNQ8JW-6nbMSaXgCOGl4Ajg%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=3da0d3fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2016年張名雅結婚，與她同屆的亞軍黃心穎、湯洛雯、岑杏賢、林泳淘及陳潔玲均在獲邀名單之上，獨欠季軍朱千雪，然而最後亦只有岑杏賢及陳潔玲出現。黃心穎解釋當日正為香港先生選舉綵排，對被忽略的朱三緘其口。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/chu_fp_7230292195ba1f96d6e664-1050x550.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2Fchu_fp_7230292195ba1f96d6e664-1050x550.png&h=d91bc3fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近年冠軍張名雅在娛圈半紅不黑，仕途一般載浮載沉，今日黃心穎又被揭一腳踏兩船的驚世醜聞；季軍朱千雪，反而觀眾緣最為強盛，即使短暫淡出專心學業支持者亦絲毫不減，「民選冠軍」美譽果然名不虛傳。"},{"pid":"d182d8016212c5c897ba55f6e53136e2102ff0c9","tid":1109424,"uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"張名雅拍親都大茄，霉到"},{"pid":"52fe4dba4b605ec3019d778806a5c89a5e17ef6e","tid":1109424,"uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2325000/2327964/49047656_2280994132135323_5240103926413393920_o_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2325000%2F2327964%2F49047656_2280994132135323_5240103926413393920_o_1024.jpg&h=021cf430&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張名雅在2016年與拍拖1年半的律師男友）結婚，翌年3月誕下兒子蔡浚鏗（Mario），2018年再宣布懷孕4個月。 張名雅一直較以家庭為重，也不是太受大台重用，入行以在劇集都是當配角。對於「安心偷食」，張名雅在IG留言：「呢個世界實在太多誘惑。大家都知道是錯的，但都會選擇犯錯。Mi，你要加油，活得更好。」本身也為人妻的張名雅表態支持Sammi。"},{"pid":"c8d5049053ff3c42fff24b89d66cb5c080e83fb8","tid":1109424,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d182d8016212c5c897ba55f6e53136e2102ff0c9","tid":1109424,"uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"張名雅拍親都大茄，霉到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:10:36.000Z","msg":"可能蔡太太嬌小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd60057c1ab61b36ab10a33afd779ab3d82a419","tid":1109424,"uid":177965,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:22:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e689e2ba393a7f3e603761710b30518345de8894","tid":1109424,"uid":33872,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cfd60057c1ab61b36ab10a33afd779ab3d82a419","tid":1109424,"uid":177965,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:22:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:26:18.000Z","msg":"佢唔係讀書咩？"},{"pid":"906bd9dfcda5f8a144e93da0c80fbc264b97c6a3","tid":1109424,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8d5049053ff3c42fff24b89d66cb5c080e83fb8","tid":1109424,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d182d8016212c5c897ba55f6e53136e2102ff0c9","tid":1109424,"uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"張名雅拍親都大茄，霉到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:10:36.000Z","msg":"可能蔡太太嬌小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:20:37.000Z","msg":"樣子唔出眾就要靠演技<br />\n兩樣都冇真係等運到"}]}